{
  "texts": [
    "Data privacy and security emerged as another critical concern amongst participants.",
    "GPT technologies, by their very nature, necessitate the use of voluminous data to generate responses, make recommendations, or create content.",
    "In the tourism industry, where customer data is often sensitive and bound by stringent data protection regulations, the challenge of ensuring that GPT technologies are compliant with these regulations is paramount.",
    "Furthermore, the ethical use of customer data, and ensuring transparency in how artificial intelligence makes decisions, is a pivotal concern that many participants highlighted.",
    "Such concerns not only stem from a regulatory perspective but also touch upon building and maintaining customer trust, which is integral to sustained business relationships."
  ]
}